title: Birguaali Kannada Audio 2009
description:
Starring Chethan , Vaidya and Tara - Birugaali Songs Latest Kannada MP3 - Birugaali Kannada Songs New - Download MP3

Upcoming Kannada actor Chetan, who debuted with Aa Dinagalu based on noted writer Agni Shridhar's book 'Daadaagiriya Dinagalu', is all set to make a trendy appearance soon in his next film Beerugaali, directed by choreographer-turned-director Harsha of Geleya fame and produced by Patil Shahapoor. Chetan is currently working on building a six-pack! During the recent audio launch of Beerugaali, director Harsha hinted that Chetan is working hard to change his looks, body structure and even the body language for his role in Beerugaali, produced with a budget of Rs. 3 crores. He also said that Beerugaali would showcase Chethan's fighting and dancing abilities. Anyway, we are anxiously waiting to see Chetan's six pack abs on screen.The two songs shot in Greece and one fight shot in deep water are the biggest highlights of Beerugaali. Venu wields the camera. Harsha handles the story and screenplay also.
